        },
        {
          "text": "The teaching staff the lecturer faculty  members were very good.",
          "name": "Priya Gupta",
          "course_tag_name": "L.L.B"
        },
        {
          "text": "College is well mentained and academic wise is also very nice",
          "name": "Sadiya khatoon",
          "course_tag_name": "BA"
        },
        {
          "text": "Teachers are cooperative and are always ready to help",
