          "course_tag_name": "BA"
        },
        {
          "text": "They are more focused on academic but do not give practical knowledge",
          "name": "Sadiya khatoon",
          "course_tag_name": "BA"
        },
        {
          "text": "Canteen is very unhygienic, once I ate a something and i got typhoid",
          "name": "Sadiya khatoon",
          "course_tag_name": "BA"
        },
        {
          "text": "there is just one thing that i dont like is messy garden in front of tagore liberary, people spend more time there instead of their classroom.",
